        <ul>
          <li>Transactional emails (purchase confirmation, download links)</li>
          <li>Product update notifications</li>
          <li>Newsletter content (if subscribed — you can unsubscribe at any time)</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We will never sell your email address to third parties.</p>

        <h2>11. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of the United States. Any disputes shall be resolved in the courts of the State of Texas.</p>

        <h2>12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
